data.output: Looking for headphones that will let you enjoy your music to the fullest? Check out the JBL C100SI! These in-ear headphones are designed to provide JBL pure bass, so you can enjoy punchy bass and rock music the way it was meant to be heard. The one-button remote lets you control your music with ease, and the angled buds provide comfort and a fit that won't let you down. Plus, the black color looks great with any outfit. If you're not satisfied with the C100SI, JBL offers a 30-day replacement warranty. And with worldwide free shipping, you can get your new headphones delivered right to your door.
